    @( The square root of 2 is bounded by 1 and 2.  (Contributed by Roy F.
       Longton, 8-Aug-2005.) @)
    sqr2gt1lt2ROY @p |- ( 1 < ( sqr ` 2 ) /\ ( sqr ` 2 ) < 2 ) @=
